original: Dahl, Göran Oskar, bankdirektör, Värnamo, f. 10/9/95 i Växjö. — Stud:-ex. i Växjö 14. Anst. i Sydsv. Kre-ditbol. 14-22, i Skånska banken 22, kont.xhef f. dess kont. i Lamhult 25-42, dir. o. kont xhef i Värnamo fr. 42.
translated: Dahl, Göran Oskar, bank director, Värnamo, b. 10/9/95 in Växjö. - High-school graduate in Växjö in 1914. Employed at Sydsvenska Kreditbolaget from 1914-1922, at Skånska banken in 1922, head of department for its branch in Lamhult from 1925-1942, director and head of department in Värnamo since 1942.
